    <briefdescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classNavigationPlugin" kindref="compound">NavigationPlugin</ref> class ED plugin for publishing a map for navigation The objects, walls and furniture, in the current world model, which are inbetween specified heights, are down-projected. The result is published as a occupancy grid. </para>    </briefdescription>
